title: Kumari 21F audio to be launched by month end
text: Kumari 21F is an upcoming romantic tale starring Raj Tarun and Hebah Patel in the lead roles. As per the latest reports, the makers are planning to unveil the audio during this month end. An official confirmation will be released during this news. Devi Sri Prasad is the music composer and Ratnavelu is the cinematographer. Creative film maker Sukumar is the producer for the film and Palnati Surya Pratap has directed it. Currently, the post production works are going on at a brisk pace.
